\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}BOX 1 \'96 Seeker\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You wouldn\'92t call yourself a Christian\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t know if you would buy into the whole God thing\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You might even think some of the things we do or talk about is a little weird\'85that\'92s ok!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We created this church for you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But let me tell you something \'96 you think you are seeking God but really God is coming after you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}One of the biggest push backs people have is God wants something from me\'85you\'92re right \'96 He wants your sin, He wants your doubt, He wants your pain, and wants to replace your past with something better. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And until you realize that your next step with God is actually what will free you, you will continue to be stuck where you are spiritually.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
