\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Until we embrace the Gospel as a gift card instead of something you have to work toward \cf6 (or earn)\cf0  you will never be able to receive what God has for you. \
